<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">He was gone for 6 months after the wedding. She was 4 months pregnant when married. He was still around trying to get Reggie to call off the marriage <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">He was gone for 6 months after the wedding. She was 4 months pregnant when married. He was still around trying to get Reggie to call off the marriage after the deflowering.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
